source.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Displays
source.description: This list contains all currently ENERGY STAR certified displays. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at https://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=monitors.pr_crit_monitors.

datasets.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Displays
datasets.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 6.0 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Displays that are effective as of June 1, 2013. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at https://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=monitors.pr_crit_monitors.
